@@ -0,0 +1,40 @@
+<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
+<manifest xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android"
+    package="edu.hzuapps.androidlabs.homeworks.net1414080903114"
+    android:versionCode="1"
+    android:versionName="1.0" >
+
+    <uses-sdk
+        android:minSdkVersion="16"
+        android:targetSdkVersion="21" />
+
+    <application
+        android:allowBackup="true"
+        android:icon="@drawable/ic_launcher"
+        android:label="@string/app_name"
+        android:theme="@style/AppTheme" >
+        <activity
+            android:name=".MainActivity"
+            android:label="@string/app_name" >
+            <intent-filter>
+                <action android:name="android.intent.action.MAIN" />
+
+                <category android:name="android.intent.category.LAUNCHER" />
+            </intent-filter>
+        </activity>
+        <activity
+            android:name=".Net1414080903114Activity"
+            android:label="@string/app_name" >
+            
+        </activity>
+        <activity
+            android:name=".DiskActivity"
+            android:label="I am Diskctivity">
+        </activity>
+        <activity
+            android:name=".NetworkActivity"
+            android:label="I am Networkctivity">
+        </activity>
+    </application>
+
+</manifest>

@@ -0,0 +1,11 @@
+<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
+<LinearLayout xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android"
+    android:layout_width="match_parent"
+    android:layout_height="match_parent"
+    android:orientation="vertical" >
+    
+	<TextView
+        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
+        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
+        android:text="@string/disk_hello" />
+</LinearLayout>

@@ -0,0 +1,27 @@
+<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
+<RelativeLayout xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android"
+    android:layout_width="match_parent"
+    android:layout_height="match_parent" >
+    
+	<TextView
+        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
+        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
+        android:text="@string/net_hello" />
+	<Button
+        android:id="@+id/diskBtn"
+        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
+        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
+        android:layout_alignParentBottom="true"
+        android:layout_alignParentLeft="true"
+        android:onClick="clickDisk"
+        android:text="@string/start_disk_activity"/>
+
+    <Button
+        android:id="@+id/networkBtn"
+        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
+        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
+        android:layout_alignParentBottom="true"
+        android:layout_alignParentRight="true"
+        android:onClick="clickNetwork"
+        android:text="@string/start_network_activity"/>
+</RelativeLayout>

@@ -0,0 +1,10 @@
+<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
